These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, may, february
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Birthday   | april | september | may | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, mauve, pink, chestnut
1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
3. the person who likes pink is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Color   | mauve | brown | chestnut | pink |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, ambient, house, electronic
1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
2. the fan of trance is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance | house | ambient | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, may, july, october
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Birthday   | may | march | october | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, november, september, february
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Birthday   | february | september | november | august |

