.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
House: palace, art-deco, modern, gothic-revival
1. the palace house is on the left of the modern house##1
2. the modern house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
3. the art-deco house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the art-deco house is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| House   | palace | modern | art-deco | gothic-revival |

