.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, skydiving, puzzles, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | gardening | skydiving | rock-climbing | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-11::.
