2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Transport   | ship | jet-ski | motorbike | airplane |

